{"title":"东风把红云漫卷（外一首）","authors":["沙鸥"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风把红云漫卷（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙鸥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风把红云漫卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红光擦亮了莽山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来过这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山河改变了容颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们亲切地谈论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在工地、在路边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的时刻永远难忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见毛主席那么康健。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的笑声还在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锹上留下他的温暖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看今夜拦河大坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将猛升三尺三！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王偷看拦河坝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王出了水晶殿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急忙奔，脚步乱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨开云头向下瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大吃一惊直冒汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三陵，景色变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东西山头看不见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦河大坝挡着路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比大山被腰斩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听机器轰隆响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见人马千千万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小斗车，像长蛇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条直奔大坝前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万方砂石万担土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推的推来担的担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传送皮带像瀑布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砂土送到坝上面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊脚碾，大夯板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来去碾压山抖颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦河大坝日夜长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看就要长上天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王看得肝胆裂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青筋满额腿发软，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正想回宫办后事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽闻滚雷震群山："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“鼓足干劲战三日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日上土方破五万！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见欢呼盖大坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗翻转映云天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风吹得劲如火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人如潮涌汗如泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心本来比天大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑坝计划定提前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王挥泪叹三声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怪自己走得慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催逼洪水已无用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大门已被铁手关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此群龙困水库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万箭穿心不敢看…"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}